room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped!" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: Our first time participating in an escape room. We did Kidnapped. It was myself, my husband and our 13 year old son. We had a blast. We loved that it was a private booking so we could enjoy the experience as a family. Highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped!" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: Had an excellent time at this escape room. The "Kidnapped" game was so much fun and a great team building experience for my co-workers and I. I highly recommend The Breakout Room to everyone! The staff was also very friendly and hilarious!
